                                MLink 1.2

                       Created by Charles-N. Jacob

  MLink is a @{" Workbench game " link play} that is based on the well known
puzzle where you try to recreate four coloured chains, one in each
column in the least amount of moves. Unlike the real game, MLink's
four sides are 'flattened' on a 4 x 4 game board, but it is played
just like the original game.

